name: Three Kisses Restaurant 'N' Feni Bar

reviews.review_text:
This restaurant will take you to 90s, everywhere it’s a feel of 90s era. Food is delicious specially their Goan dishes, must try their Goan dishes.

It’s near a field area so you will find the ambience relaxing.
They have kept Color books for kids to keep them engaging, staff is polite and attentive.
The owner is very creative and joyful.

Fantastic place. Our favourite.
Tinho is so welcoming and friendly.
Tasty food. Lovely dogs. Live music was great on a Sunday. Don't miss this place.

Went for a quick lunch to this place this time in Goa. Checking their menu got excited to see Prawns caldine because we had a lovely creamy one in Candolim, got horribly disappointed with what they served. It was watery (with no flavour of coconut milk or grated coconut- only turmeric taste). Please don't order caldine here. Plus there were a lot of flies around which was a downer.
Otherwise ambience is chill with good music and there are two very friendly dogs to pet.

description:
**Three Kisses Restaurant 'N' Feni Bar: A Culinary Journey to the 90s**

Nestled in the serene surroundings of Cansaulim, Three Kisses Restaurant 'N' Feni Bar beckons diners with an impressive rating of 4.3 from nearly 900 reviews, making it a beloved local gem. Patrons frequently mention highlights such as the delectable **Goan dishes**, **fish thali**, and comforting **beef roast**, alongside the charming presence of **pet-friendly** spaces where gentle dogs roam. With tags like **squid** and **beef roast** appearing prominently in customer feedback, it's clear that the menu is designed to cater to diverse palates.

**Ambiance & Design**

As you step into Three Kisses, you are transported back to the vibrant 90s—a theme that permeates the décor and overall vibe of the establishment. The warm, inviting atmosphere features nostalgic touches that create a relaxing space, accentuated by the lovely field view outdoors. Sunlight filters through the windows, casting a golden hue on the colorful table settings reminiscent of playful times. Live music adds to the charm, particularly during weekends, enhancing the laid-back feel perfect for a leisurely meal. 

Reviews frequently praise the restaurant for its thoughtful touches such as providing coloring books for children—adding a family-friendly element to the experience. The friendly dogs that greet visitors contribute to a homely touch that makes dining here feel even more special.

![Cozy Ambiance](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdnBMt2alxuyRm7U9UKKFhpSEDpGeG_9rAyPCkF5nV2y8-HUJ6b7i92aRXr1OPT1WfSoo45vSSAKdlVaiVFiQUkFy3q0W3uOkvCgFWmg-bp8dRU4nwiyO-J5_N7xCk-qsg=w375-h281-p)

**Menu & Culinary Experience**

The menu at Three Kisses leans heavily on authentic Goan cuisine, delighting patrons with its vibrant flavors and satisfying portions. Customers particularly rave about the **beef roast**, known for its tender meat and rich spices, as well as the fish thali—an ensemble of expertly prepared seafood that reflects the coastal heritage of the region. However, a mixed review highlights the **Prawns Caldine**, suggesting inconsistency in execution, with a critique on the dish lacking the anticipated creaminess and flavor.

Presentation is indeed appealing, with dishes served in earthy tones that complement the flavorful offerings. Diners will also appreciate the availability of pet-friendly options, making it a great outing for families and their beloved furry companions.

![Delicious Food Presentation](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdmYZ_n550xduJ6TH8C6JnqQBIa9Bqayn_EQTtXB_Bc0R6jEhzSMHfXDFAv13yIyZrM5FeoiCEBwncdZs08vlc7vWATA8X8UvEO0RhICDm3HxyXXrbd-Ik7msWcl98OmQwutMjMw=w375-h563-p)

**Customer Experience & Service**

Feedback consistently highlights the commendable service at Three Kisses, particularly praising staff member Tinho for his warmth and attentiveness. Guests mention that the personnel are polite and readily available, making the dining experience enjoyable and seamless. Whether you choose to make a reservation or opt for a walk-in, expect a welcoming environment that strives to make you feel at home.

**Popularity & Reviews**

With 901 reviews contributing to its solid rating, Three Kisses has garnered a positive reputation not just from locals but also tourists seeking an authentic Goan experience. While a few diners reported issues with specific dishes, the overall sentiment is overwhelmingly favorable, with mentions of delightful live music and a charming atmosphere that enhance the experience. 

**Utilizing Visual Content**

Photos shared by customers vividly depict the cheerful ambiance, from vibrant plates filled with well-prepared Goan specialties to snapshots of furry friends lounging in the restaurant. These images reinforce the comforting vibe of the space and the joy that comes from a meal shared amongst family and friends.

![Pet-Friendly Enjoyment](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdlU4EyuXmJYcgskvnDwBH1ANpoE35Wo26nDCePeIuAu_ShCaKzTK2Xhfnyy_HCeu9-VKSctaQYG3J9L3r4me3gv3RyFcQMhvacbemmfWorgTO-kZmbx5j4bAV1M-1RQ_vBxAfuYfA=w750-h563-p)

In summary, Three Kisses Restaurant 'N' Feni Bar is more than just a dining spot; it’s a nostalgic retreat that serves mouthwatering Goan cuisine in a friendly, relaxed setting. With its playful ambiance, flavorful menu, and attentive service, it captures the essence of joyful dining—making it a must-visit for anyone exploring the area.
